msgstr ""

#. [option]: speaker=Arne
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/2_The_Chase.cfg:458
msgid "Oh, all right then. Come along with us."
msgstr "או, אז בסדר. בואו יחד איתנו."

#. [message]: speaker=Brena
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/2_The_Chase.cfg:462
msgid "Thank you. My comrades and I will help you on your noble quest."
msgstr "תודה לך. אחי לנשק ואני נעזור לך במשימתך האצילה."

#. [option]: speaker=Arne
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/2_The_Chase.cfg:470
msgid "I am sorry. We have not the time to spare."
msgstr "אני מצטער. אין לנו זמן להתעכב."

#. [message]: speaker=Brena
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/2_The_Chase.cfg:474
msgid ""
"Take this, then, for I see that you are on a quest. My comrades will help "
"you whenever you call for them."
msgstr ""
"אז, קח את זה, כי אני רואה שאתה במשימה. אחי לנשק יעזרו לך מתי שתקרא להם."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/2_The_Chase.cfg:491
msgid "You receive 70 pieces of gold!"
msgstr "קיבלת 70 פיסות זהב!"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/2_The_Chase.cfg:511
msgid "My reinforcements are here!"
msgstr "התגבורת שלי הגיעה!"

#. [message]: speaker=Arne
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/2_The_Chase.cfg:515
msgid "He escaped us..."
msgstr "הוא נמלט מאיתנו..."

#. [message]: speaker=Nil-Galion
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/2_The_Chase.cfg:526
msgid ""
"You foolish human, you killed me but you won't be able to reach the undead "
"in time. I fulfilled the contract and will be reanimated soon to become a "
"lord of their armies."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arne
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/2_The_Chase.cfg:530
msgid ""
"Hurry, we have to track them down. Maybe we can still get them. They have to "
"be in the north!"
msgstr ""

